gh the generic aggregate implementor path instead.\n\nCovering the remaining sites would require directly invoking private internals or shadowing/changing Calcite implementation classes, which would violate the task rules.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05b46d0ed5a77673016a254991efa08195a87664fb61cbd804\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 5406, "output": 1386, "cacheRead": 69120, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 75912, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780828534221, "responseId": "resp_05b46d0ed5a77673016a25497751608195af559cefc19c7a8d"}}
